## Modern CSS Features

CSS has evolved significantly. Let's explore some powerful features:

### CSS Grid
```css
.grid-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  gap: 1rem;
}
```

### CSS Variables
```css
:root {
  --primary-color: #3498db;
  --spacing-unit: 1rem;
}

.element {
  color: var(--primary-color);
  padding: var(--spacing-unit);
}
```

### Modern Layouts
Flexbox and Grid have revolutionized web layouts. No more float hacks!

## Best Practices
- Use semantic class names
- Implement responsive design
- Optimize performance
- Maintain consistency

Stay tuned for more CSS tips and tricks!
